        6 Preparation of Digital Contents Conceptual data types is different from physical data types â€“Conceptual: humanâ€™s recognition Music, opera, dancing, art, literature, movie, construction, etc. â€“Physical: computerâ€™s recognition Text, image, audio, video, etc.







7

        7 Digital Formats for DRs Digitization principles: â€“For both preservation and service needs. â€“Multiple resolution for different goals. â€“Preservation: for long-term needs and reproduction â€“Service: for online needs and demonstration







