        24 Text Specification Textual materials as searchable text â€“Searchable text with markup: ASCII text, with TEI- conformant SGML markup â€“Document Type Definition (DTD): American Memory DTD (ammen.dtd) Textual materials reproduced as images â€“Archival or master images â€“Images for convenient access







