        37 Moving-image Materials (1) Moving-image file types: â€“Moderate resolution files: Image size: 320x240 Frame rate: 30 fps Data rate: ca. 1.2 Mbit/sec (ca. 150 Kbit/sec) Compression: MPEG-1 Format: mpg







